      <title>欧洲央行要求银行提供更多证据证明交易仍在欧洲进行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/ecb-seeks-more-proof-from-banks-that-trading-is-still-in-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行希望全球顶级证券公司提供更多证据，证明它们在欧盟境内开展与欧盟客户相关的交易，从而加强自英国脱欧以来长达数年的活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/ecb-seeks-more-proof-from-banks-that-trading-is-still-in-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 09:29:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典计划关闭六家国有 AP 养老基金中的两家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/sweden-plans-to-shutter-two-of-six-state-owned-ap-pension-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典计划将国有养老基金（统称 AP-fonderna）的数量从六个削减至四个，以提高基金管理者的成本效益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/sweden-plans-to-shutter-two-of-six-state-owned-ap-pension-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 09:26:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国债券市场因税收问题准备迎接零售投资热潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/uk-bond-market-readies-for-retail-investment-rush-on-tax-quirk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在英国富人为了降低税收而纷纷赎回英国债券后，投资者正准备迎接大量散户现金涌入英国政府债券市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/uk-bond-market-readies-for-retail-investment-rush-on-tax-quirk</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 09:24:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非电力公司停电威胁重现，兰特和债券下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/rand-and-bonds-fall-as-specter-of-eskom-blackouts-returns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非国有电力公司警告称，可能会在 10 个多月内首次实施断电，这可能对努力摆脱多年停滞的南非经济造成打击。此后，南非兰特和债券价格暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/rand-and-bonds-fall-as-specter-of-eskom-blackouts-returns</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 09:23:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚电力受强势先令推动宣布中期股息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/kenya-power-declares-interim-dividend-bouyed-by-strong-shilling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚国营电力公司将在当地货币走强后九年来首次派发中期股息，大幅削减其贷款偿还成本。股价一度上涨 33%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/kenya-power-declares-interim-dividend-bouyed-by-strong-shilling</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 09:20:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国风电发电量下降，可再生能源发电利润面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/german-wind-output-sinks-risking-profit-at-renewable-generators</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年冬季，德国风电发电量已降至四年来的最低水平，预计周末将再次出现风速较低的情况，威胁可再生能源运营的利润。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/german-wind-output-sinks-risking-profit-at-renewable-generators</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 09:14:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非电力公司 Eskom 警告电力故障后可能造成断电风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/eskom-warns-of-south-africa-power-cuts-as-it-depletes-reserves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非国家电力公司表示，在多座电厂发生故障后，停电风险“很高”，这一警告可能会结束连续 10 个月的稳定电力供应。兰特走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/eskom-warns-of-south-africa-power-cuts-as-it-depletes-reserves</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 08:42:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼称美国“肯定”会废除煤炭气候计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/indonesia-says-climate-plan-certain-to-be-scrapped-by-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[东南亚国家的气候特使表示，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普“肯定”会废除让印度尼西亚逐步摆脱煤炭依赖的国际协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/indonesia-says-climate-plan-certain-to-be-scrapped-by-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 08:32:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Orsted 未能扭转风电行业颓势，更换首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/orsted-ceo-steps-down-after-failing-to-turn-around-wind-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在过去几年中，大西洋两岸发生了一系列巨额减记，股价也大幅下跌，麦兹·尼珀 (Mads Nipper) 将辞去丹麦风电开发商 Orsted A/S 首席执行官一职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/orsted-ceo-steps-down-after-failing-to-turn-around-wind-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 07:16:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾股市因经济增长忧虑进入熊市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/philippine-benchmark-index-declines-20-from-october-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心潜在的全球逆风和令人失望的国内经济数据，菲律宾股市连续第五天下跌，导致该国基准指数进入熊市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/philippine-benchmark-index-declines-20-from-october-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 05:37:56 GMT</pubDate>
